%article.dataset
  %section.intro
    %div.left
      %img{ :src => '/images/block.png' }
      %p
        Block is a small JavaScript library for wrapping visual components. It aims to simplify
        wiring components together, constructing interactive visuals, extending visual components
        and controlling complex styling.
